# Brand Colors and Referral Links

- Use semantic color tokens from `app/globals.css` (`bg-primary`, `text-primary`, `border-primary`, `border-border`, `text-muted-foreground`) instead of hardcoded hex values in components.
- Primary branded actions, icons, and CTAs must use `primary` tokens unless a specific design exception is requested.
- Avoid vendor-mismatched branding in UI copy, links, or assets.
- For referral link UI in this project, use Upstox-branded URLs (not competitor domains).
- Keep new UI consistent with existing token-based light/dark behavior.

